summary:
Highly motivated Mathematics-Informatics student, with outstanding results in math team competitions, in which I developed valuable leader-ship and organization skills. While seeking the pursuit of relevant knowledge I developed self-thought skills in order to design my own web page in HTML and CSS.
I am a collaborative, hardworking and adaptable person who is keen to learn new skills and welcome new challenges which I meet [creatively, imaginatively, with curiosity, flexibly, resourcefully]. 
I show effectiveness while learning, I choose quality over quantity and plan everything I do thoroughly in order to engage both intellectually and socially and accomplish/meet all my targets.
